{"title":"新民歌选","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":5,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"新民歌选"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我来了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上没有玉皇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地上没有龙王，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我就是玉皇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我就是龙王，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喝令三山五岭开道："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我来了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（陕西安康）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指路明灯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树上喜鹊喳喳地叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉咧嘴忍不住的笑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农业发展纲要四十条，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好比四十颗太阳当头照。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳也比不上它温暖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处地方它都照到。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放近耳朵听一听，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫不是毛主席的说话声？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回头胸上贴一贴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"句句话它暖人心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没闭住嘴巴笑出了声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱社员有了指路的大明灯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（江苏）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过长江"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万斤地瓜千斤粮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坐着火箭过长江。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白米要到天上收"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"层层梯田像高楼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"离天只有九尺九，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半截伸在云里头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白米要到天上收。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（湖北郧县）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨天我走东村过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨天我走东村过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家家门上挂了锁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留下黄狗汪汪叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留下公鸡在唱歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大门板上纸一张，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛笔写字字不多："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我社要搞千斤社，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有闲人家中坐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲朋要会村里人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只好等到日头落”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（湖南衡阳）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹拉弹唱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产战斗在田间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹拉弹唱地头边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘴里唱着梆子腔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里想着共产党。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（河南禹县）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想娘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"久不见娘心想娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回家见娘也平常，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"睡到半夜心又急，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明日社里要挑塘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（安徽肥西）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妹挑担子紧紧追"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"情哥挑堤快如飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妹挑担子紧紧追，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是飞进白云里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也要拼命赶上你。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（湖北麻城）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}